msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Ah, Kiryu-san!\r\nWe been waiting fer ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "It's finally time to take on the Thunders' farm team."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Ahhh, I'm gettin' nervous...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Hey now.\r\nLet's not get nervous playing 'gainst a farm team."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Moritsuka... You're looking the part."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Yeah well... I think I'd look even\r\nsnappier in a major league uniform..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "But, I s'pose this suits me fer now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Show us what you got today, all right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Yeah, y'won't regret bringin' me aboard.\r\nSo... Let's crush 'em."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Well well, greetings, my Warriors friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Huh? Why're you here, Hamana?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Whoa, let's not get snotty, now.\r\nI cleared my calendar t'see this dog n' pony show."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "I jus' wanted t'burn the look on yer faces\r\nwhen y'lose to my farm team into my mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Ha, always the jackass, Hamana."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Funny hearin' that from a guy drunk\r\noutta his socks 'til yesterday."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "You promised, we'll play the real Thunders\r\nonce we beat yer farm team today, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I promised.\r\nBut, y'gotta beat 'em first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Second string or not, they're still Thunders.\r\nAnd they don't lose to losers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "If y'think y'can beat em, shall we get goin'?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "More than happy to!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "I'll be watchin' the show from\r\nthe dugout. Best o' luck to ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "We can't lose this one...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Yeah... Let's humiliate 'em."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, when yer ready,\r\njust come lemme know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Let's figure out the batting lineup and\r\nfield positions, then start the game!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Let's win this one!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "W-We lost..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Really? You guys lost?\r\nWhat happened t'all that trash talk earlier, hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Damn, guys. I didn't think a team\r\ncould even be this bad!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Well, the farm team'll be here if y'ever\r\nwant a rematch! Try as many times as y'want!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Maybe you'll even be a little less pathetic\r\nnext time..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Let's train and gather more players...\r\nThen we can try again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "I won't let it end like this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Yeah, you're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "We did it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Yeaaaahhh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Hell yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "All right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, we did it!\r\nOur first victory as the reborn Warriors!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Yeah, we did it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Aw yeah!\r\nI'm crackin' open a cold one tonight!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Amazing... I forgot what it was like t'win...\r\nI guess we're capable if we put in the work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Thank you, Kiryu-san...\r\nWe owe a lot of this win to you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Baseball is a team sport.\r\nIt wasn't just me. We won together, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san...! Yes!\r\nWe're all winners today!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Dipshits!\r\nHow'd ya'll lose to a team this pathetic!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "W-We're sorry...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Screw it! Y'boys owe me some laps!\r\nGet a move on, right now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Not too shabby... Setouchi Warriors...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Don't forget your promise.\r\nThe next game is against the real Thunders!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "That's fine.\r\nMaybe you'll make a nice warm-up fer us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Still... Don't expect us t'go down like\r\nthese second string rejects."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Thunder... always brings the noise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... He's right, the second string\r\nThunders don't hold a candle to the main team."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "We should gather more players, train 'em up,\r\nand get in some practice games before that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Yeah, let's do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Hey! Chiba-san! Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Since we got our first victory...\r\nWe gotta celebrate with some drinks!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Get a move on! I'm feelin' great,\r\nso it's my treat tonight!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Damn, that's mighty generous!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "But the next match'll be tough...\r\nWe can't go drinkin'... Right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Nah, let them celebrate, Chiba.\r\nIt's important to remember the taste of victory."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "I-Is that so?\r\nYeah, I guess you're right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "We'll be there soon!\r\nKiryu-san, let's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "All right, let's keep up the momentum!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "That was a riot.\r\nThe team's gettin' fired up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Whoa, one too many fer me.\r\nBut tomorrow we hit the field hard!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "We do gotta practice!\r\nI wanna keep winnin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "All right, I'm gonna take off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "No prob, Kiryu-san!\r\nThanks for everything!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Our next opponent is the Thunders proper...\r\nThey talk so much trash, I wanna beat 'em!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "I'll do everything in my power...\r\nSo stay with us a while, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Yeah, of course."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Nice! I'll see ya on the field then,\r\nKiryu-san! Later!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Heh, Chiba sounds like he's\r\nfloating on air now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "Victory drinks tasted great tonight...\r\nWhen we beat that punk, they'll be even better."
msgstr ""

